doc.previous: The sum of friction drag and pressure form drag is called viscous drag This drag component takes into account the influence of viscosity In a thermodynamic perspective viscous effects represent irreversible phenomena and therefore they create entropy The calculated viscous drag use entropy changes to accurately predict the drag force
